{"word":"G4445 - πυρέσσω - pyréssō - poo-res'-so - Be sick of a fever","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πυρέσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pyréssō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">poo-res'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be sick of a fever</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஜுரமாய்க் கிட"},{"paragraph":"to be sick with a fever"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4443 - πυρά - pyrá - poo-rah'/4443\">G4443</a>; to be <i>on fire</i>, that is, (specifically) to <i>have a fever:</i> - be sick of a fever.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4445/4445\">G4445</a>, <a href=\"#/G4446/4446\">G4446</a>, <a href=\"#/G546/546\">G546</a>"}]}